1 WHEREAS, a portion of the proceeds from Brave Bella Bead Co. sales supports
2 childhood cancer awareness and research, including causes connected to St. Jude Children's
3 Research Hospital, where Bella continues to receive care; and
4 WHEREAS, Bella's inspiring testimony, entrepreneurial success, and commitment
5 to helping others have made her a beacon of hope for children and families facing adversity;
6 and
7 WHEREAS, Bella continues to use her platform to encourage others to never give
8 up on their dreams and to remain faithful and determined through life's challenges; and
9 WHEREAS, it is fitting to recognize Bella Cervantes for her exceptional courage,
10 leadership, compassion, and service to her community.
11 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
12 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Bella Cervantes, founder of Brave Bella
13 Bead Co., for her inspirational example of resilience and entrepreneurship and does hereby
14 extend best wishes for continued success, health, and happiness in all her future endeavors.
